":"Wo ist mein Handy?","en":"Where's my phone?","a":"n_3f087bb87c3d.mp3"},{"t":"Ich seh dich nicht gut.","en":"I can't see you well.","a":"n_65e5571483f5.mp3"},{"t":"Bis später.","en":"I'll see you later.","a":"n_c9ed1e43ac77.mp3"},{"t":"Heute steh ich spät auf.","en":"Today I'm getting up late.","a":"n_a684a048e741.mp3"},{"t":"Morgen steh ich früh auf.","en":"Tomorrow I'm getting up early.","a":"n_2f92c0d2d450.mp3"},{"t":"Ich weiß nicht, was ich nehmen soll.","en":"I don't know what to order.","a":"n_80a0fb39d60a.mp3"},{"t":"Was nimmst du?","en":"What are you going to order?","a":"n_80b3bb5a9570.mp3"},{"t":"Mir ist nach Schlafen.","en":"I feel like sleeping.","a":"n_233eb62e5bc0.mp3"},{"t":"Hast du Lust auszugehen?","en":"Do you feel like going out?","a":"n_465870ba340b.mp3"},{"t":"Was kostet das Wasser?","en":"How much is the water?","a":"n_e3843c2eb059.mp3"},{"t":"Wir sind in der Küche.","en":"We're in the kitchen.","a":"n_0435972a8256.mp3"},{"t":"Ich würde gern mehr lernen.","en":"I'd like to learn more.","a":"n_f93f6d09add5.mp3"},{"t":"Das solltest du nicht tun.","en":"You shouldn't do that.","a":"n_3f0eef591644.mp3"},{"t":"Du solltest nicht so viel arbeiten.","en":"You shouldn't work so much.","a":"n_00f69b4c1201.mp3"},{"t":"Warum kommst du nicht?","en":"Why aren't you coming?","a":"n_75f837d96e44.mp3"},{"t":"Wann kommst du?","en":"What time are you coming?","a":"n_846a8c561163.mp3"},{"t":"Ist es nah oder weit?","en":"Is it close or far?","a":"n_9f0b1129d543.mp3"},{"t":"Der Zug ist billig.","en":"The train is cheap.","a":"n_c9d438038ceb.mp3"},{"t":"Der Zug ist weit weg.","en":"The train is far.","a":"n_c6e386e13be5.mp3"},{"t":"Hast du was Billigeres?","en":"Do you have anything cheaper?","a":"n_1d75edc5fbbd.mp3"},{"t":"Ich bin's wieder.","en":"It's me again.","a":"n_6091d14c21d6.mp3"},{"t":"Ich bin in fünf Minuten da.","en":"I'll be there in five minutes.","a":"n_ab59b60da97d.mp3"},{"t":"Ich geh gern mit dir aus.","en":"I like going out with you.","a":"n_7681e